Package: sheafq
Title: Vector-Valued Sheaf Q Tests for Multi-Trait Heterogeneity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Elliot", "Tower", email = "elliot@elliottower.ai",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the vector-valued sheaf Q statistic for detecting
    effect vector rotation in multi-ancestry, multi-trait meta-analyses.
    On scalar stalks (d=1), sheaf Q reduces algebraically to Cochran's Q.
    On vector-valued stalks (d>1), the multivariate sheaf Q detects
    coordinated heterogeneity patterns—such as effect vector rotation—that
    d independent scalar Q tests cannot detect. Includes locus classification
    (concordant, rotation-only, component-only) and rotation angle computation.
